/ Typography Extendables
%section#typography.element-group
  %h1.section-title Typography Extendables
  %p.intro
    :markdown
      Silent extendables for general typography.

      Remove if you don't need them. Add your own as needed.
  %div#serif.element
    %h2.element-title
      %a.permalink{:href => "#serif"}
        serif
    .extendable-source
      / .comment
      /   :markdown
      /     - the same as `%clearfix` but class-based.
      /     - Your CMS may use this class, so let's extend it.
      /     - Remove if you don't need it.
      %pre.scss
        :preserve
          %serif {
            font-family: $font-serifs;
